Event Management Website â€” Full DevOps Project (AWS Free Tier + Terraform + Docker + EC2 + GitHub Actions)

This project demonstrates a complete DevOps workflow from source code to deployment using ONLY AWS Free Tier resources.

The application is deployed on an Amazon Linux 2 EC2 instance using Docker, and every push to GitHub automatically triggers CI/CD deployment via GitHub Actions.

